# Deny-by-default: the only root-context Docker builds are frontend/, portal/
# and docs/ (workspace images). Everything else — especially env files with
# secrets (compose/.env*), infra/, and Terraform state — stays out of the
# build context stream.
*
!pnpm-workspace.yaml
!package.json
!pnpm-lock.yaml
!tsconfig.base.json
!frontend
!portal
!docs
!packages
# Re-deny heavy/generated paths inside the allowed trees
frontend/node_modules
portal/node_modules
docs/node_modules
packages/*/node_modules
frontend/.next
portal/.next
docs/.next
docs/out
frontend/test-results
portal/test-results
frontend/playwright-report
portal/playwright-report
**/.env*
